* Not living objects
* Specify resources in map file (fruits, wood, water and so on)
* Action animations
* Load animations info file
* Thread the map, tileset, animation, and resources loading
* Display the loadingscreen before loading the GamePlay class

BUGS:

* When choosing settings at the in game screen and then quiting from it,
    the gameplay class loads again.
* When pressing esc in the game to open the in game menu, the background
    is not the same as the last view of the gameplay.
